text: Theoharis Trasha (born April 21, 1985 in Elbasan) is an Albanian weightlifter, who with his younger brother Gert Trasha competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics in Athens, where he finished 12th.Sports-Reference Profile == References == Category:Albanian male weightlifters Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic weightlifters of Albania Category:Weightlifters at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Elbasan
title: Theoharis Trasha
